text: Walter Thiel (7 March 1949 in Treysa, Hesse - 23 August 2019) was a German theoretical chemist. He was the president of the World Association of Theoretical and Computational Chemists (WATOC) from 2011. == References == ==Other websites== *Homepage of the Thiel group at the MPI for Coal Research Category:1949 births Category:2019 deaths Category:German chemists
